      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.YMGOKoZtKgJqIsAD]{Mechanic Trick}</p>\n<p>Sometimes it’s imperative to get a device working again as quickly as possible. With this mechanic trick, you can attempt to repair an item as a move action. The item has a chance to fail on each usage equal to 100 – ten times your Intelligence modifier. If a jury-rigged item fails, it takes twice as long as normal to repair it, and you can’t use this mechanic trick on it again.</p>"
